        "lang": "en",
        "text": "His son by the slave woman was born according to the flesh, but his son by the free woman was born as the result of a divine promise."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "The son of the slave wife was born in a human attempt to bring about the fulfillment of God’s promise. But the son of the freeborn wife was born as God’s own fulfillment of his promise."
      }
